      <body>before_validation_on_create and before_validation_on_update methods are available. The syntax has changed.

@@@ ruby
  before_validation(:on =&gt; :create){ do_something }
  before_validation(:on =&gt; :update){ do_something }
@@@

Yes the documentation needs to be updated.</body>
